title: The Passing Boom and Week 6 Waiver Watch | The Dantasy Football Podcast (Ep. 318)
description:
The Ringer’s Danny Heifetz and Danny Kelly offer their initial advice after Week 5 (1:00), list the top guys to grab off waivers heading into Week 6 (13:00), and make sense of the passing boom of 2018 and how it will affect the players on your fantasy team (22:30).
